"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1da98a4627049b986909e693019fdb7be1e56856","tid":298251,"uid":27985,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T17:03:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我都想要個處男 佢條撚俾第二個含過我先含<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cca62063fe492fa31d44291045d0ee5ab01acddd","tid":298251,"uid":99381,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T17:41:16.000Z","msg":"會 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔係好想比個處佢 覺得唔公平 <br />\n佢有叫我含 我又唔識整痛佢佢會話都係算<br />\n佢之前都無意中講過佢ex幫佢含得好舒服<br />\n我聽到燥燥地 即刻唔想再幫佢"},{"pid":"79ef194e3bf042fcf10b1a29d0859f413a30db67","tid":298251,"uid":73722,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T17:50:37.000Z","msg":"認同樓主呢個心態<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">所以我知D女非處就唔媾，結果有女都仲係處男</span>"},{"pid":"610d8b58df64e00cfd75cf5667f5029b02916a95","tid":298251,"uid":73909,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T18:05:23.000Z","msg":"會<br />\n非常介意"},{"pid":"6117ec776afe05f5c825729ce9ee5e3ee34468b7","tid":298251,"uid":71742,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T18:12:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\n自己係處時另一半已經俾其他女玩過碌鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n次次諗起都會偷偷地唔開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n屌 係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"089e14c88bf063a7e8d0ba13a83fac3bd9c880f4","tid":298251,"uid":11030,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T18:26:48.000Z","msg":"會<br />\n處先可以破me<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/34.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac94ec9bc6371dae92664cac3e0965dc00eab888","tid":298251,"uid":47827,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T18:31:31.000Z","msg":"但係處冇技術"},{"pid":"8af0a01d05ffc77b9188ef7b5104a8d4bf9f4ed8","tid":298251,"uid":77895,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T18:33:37.000Z","msg":"真心 唔好聽連登仔講話唔係處就係雞啦<br />\n你留到結婚到冇用 依家時代唔同啦<br />\n拍拖其中一樣好緊要嘅野係性 <br />\n性方面好應該要同伴侶夾同磨合到<br />\n亦會令到你地嘅關係更親密<br />\n拍拖時期就應該要有呢個經歷，唔通結左婚發現對方冷感而自己又好有需要嗰陣先黎後悔？<br />\n只要搵到個真心鐘意，覺得佢值得比嘅人<br />\n就冇問題啦<br />\n就算散左都好，至少你曾經真係好愛過對方，你比左個處比一個值得比嘅人<br />\n要知道結婚嗰個好多時未必係你最愛嗰個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n只要唔係濫 我覺得冇問題"},{"pid":"2e41fb18118d6b348f6465907461fa515f6784bc","tid":298251,"uid":120581,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T18:55:24.000Z","msg":"會"},{"pid":"dc563dcc14f00f4bfff72df95fdb670959342a90","tid":298251,"uid":19989,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T18:56:38.000Z","msg":"介意 第一次俾咗條n手撚同第一次俾咗n手西一樣都係咁難受<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">不過俾個有經驗同有技巧嘅人lead係幾好</span>"},{"pid":"e29f675560912775872648ffe8c99b1e2de57873","tid":298251,"uid":121019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T05:29:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9db5e04f31a464cc832b9817d09fd39cee3f74d9","tid":298251,"uid":20696,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T05:34:39.000Z","msg":"會<br />\n非常介意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc4de8fbcaf39bf5255d849841aca443538b7dea","tid":298251,"uid":27793,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T07:11:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>真心 唔好聽連登仔講話唔係處就係雞啦<br />\n你留到結婚到冇用 依家時代唔同啦<br />\n拍拖其中一樣好緊要嘅野係性 <br />\n性方面好應該要同伴侶夾同磨合到<br />\n亦會令到你地嘅關係更親密<br />\n拍拖時期就應該要有呢個經歷，唔通結左婚發現對方冷感而自己又好有需要嗰陣先黎後悔？<br />\n只要搵到個真心鐘意，覺得佢值得比嘅人<br />\n就冇問題啦<br />\n就算散左都好，至少你曾經真係好愛過對方，你比左個處比一個值得比嘅人<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\">要知道結婚嗰個好多時未必係你最愛嗰個</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n只要唔係濫 我覺得冇問題</blockquote><br />\n不同意"},{"pid":"e46729dea83d5ce8c2c343742c3fea829878c786","tid":298251,"uid":8703,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T07:19:20.000Z","msg":"其實會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但都無計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 過左去既野又無得返轉頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1df5cbafe74859fdb049163a78853a7d860cea7","tid":298251,"uid":84911,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T19:38:00.000Z","msg":"屌咁好唔好同個處男一齊破處先"},{"pid":"c62bcefdef52a741a5ab54997f711303da058ef2","tid":298251,"uid":84911,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T19:38:28.000Z","msg":"ex黎 但已散 半sp關係"},{"pid":"3764cb4bd08e9e2e2d064ed35c0fbf74cc01d4b9","tid":298251,"uid":33041,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T20:13:22.000Z","msg":"會 會好唔開心<br />\n好彩男朋友同我一齊時重係處<br />\n我唔想佢同其他女仔搞過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}